{"tid":16910,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再拎開post數打飛機","createTime":"2016-12-01T15:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T03:34:56.000Z","uid":28451,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4b4a87f189cd0a7bb5db8e6a368b04e2218488f","tid":16910,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:34:09.000Z","msg":"依家上論壇吹水定跑數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時返工返學仲未夠<br />\n同香港某論壇比，post數多定少又點<br />\n事實係之前上開果個悶左，個apps又唔好用<br />\n等於去餐廳食飯，坐底睇manu唔啱食咪去第二間<br />\n你改manu, d野食好食左嘅，d人自然就會返去<br />\n唔存在咩忠誠嘅問題，冇邊個欠邊個<br />\n香港人不嬲都好現實<br />\n我相信如果呢到日後變得不思進取<br />\n而另一個論壇大大改善<br />\n果邊人流始終會升返<br />\n不過現階段，我睇唔到要上某論壇嘅理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6e77b191ada2adda7779ae05b1e1fd5404575e","tid":16910,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:35:52.000Z","msg":"你啱"},{"pid":"9cc61f59b0b2adda1b9f0e2601014bb17a8f1acd","tid":16910,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:38:26.000Z","msg":"始終到幾時"},{"pid":"6a4be83f75406b9379589bbb8bf51bcd398d79f8","tid":16910,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>始終到幾時</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能某人冇機會睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc7ebd3b408717113e4e47c4b6b059c1c61655e","tid":16910,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ddfcab416fdf6117766f39e9d4ad8515c6e240","tid":16910,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5937ab747b710cb192b42658156d6d85986ed9","tid":16910,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:31:19.000Z",